Source: cron-utils
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/Myshkouski/pg-cron-utils

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-cron-utils
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-cron-utils
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cron expression utilities for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 cron_utils provides SQL functions to parse cron expressions, test whether a
 timestamp matches an expression, and compute previous or next trigger times.
